description: Hot Diggity Dogs (and sausages) is Seattle's mobile authority on Hot Dogs! ! Standard menu grilled to order   ¼ lb Polish Sausage or All Beef Hot dog, bag of  chips and bottle water, ketchup, mustard, relish, onions. UPON REQUEST tons of types of mustards, pepperoncini, jalapeños, sauerkraut, SPECIALTY SAUSAGES/DOGS,  chicken sausages or vegetarian sausages. Or in spring and summer we can bring one of these specialties: Seattle Mariner Dogs and Johnsonville Bratwurst, ½ lb Kielbasa, UPON REQUEST BEVERAGES coffee, hot cocoa, bottle Coke, canned soda, lemonade, Gatorade.
name: Hot Diggity Dogs
